{"tid":1115052,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Denis Amy Jeremy 嘅Arrival 天煞異降","createTime":"2019-04-19T01:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T23:21:08.000Z","uid":74778,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"e24a7fedbf8c48ae03ea0bb59f9945d2c13f981c","tid":1115052,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"係我睇過最好睇既戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係連燈吹奏過nolan，nolan既電影係小說，佢講故事既能力好強。zs既電影係詩篇，同好多神話有關，直頭可以拍得出浪漫主義風格油畫既畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GesGo5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GesGo5.png&h=a6ab4fde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXGuUKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXGuUKj.png&h=cc52d037&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQ6KJCW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQ6KJCW.gif&h=12731dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/146759246757083530/BF6EBE7B2CCE7E07B3763900FEB56B6F714769E3/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F146759246757083530%2FBF6EBE7B2CCE7E07B3763900FEB56B6F714769E3%2F&h=792dee04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6564c22354be75a86e0056c7b27520e1/tumblr_ms66d3Rj2N1r0b2hgo1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6564c22354be75a86e0056c7b27520e1%2Ftumblr_ms66d3Rj2N1r0b2hgo1_400.gif&h=fad00f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-16-2015/wDnw4t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-16-2015%2FwDnw4t.gif&h=d13d601a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/MammothPrestigiousChick-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FMammothPrestigiousChick-size_restricted.gif&h=c475a7d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左今次要吹奏既係神導denis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我第一次睇佢既作品係 Blades Runner 2049<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經比佢既鏡頭同個氣氛震撼左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5xubRS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5xubRS.png&h=93b3f76b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U9uWSHWcHag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU9uWSHWcHag&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=e9201871\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U9uWSHWcHag</a><br />\n佢對美既觸覺，用慢同靜每次都令人覺得美到窒息<br />\n<br />\n同時帶出<strong>是否有人性就係人類？非自然而生既人是否俱有人性？</strong>既沈重命題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左今次既重點<strong><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Arrival</span></strong></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UYdCGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UYdCGB.png&h=6be561d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>好快講下劇情:<br />\n插敍講紅髮藍眼Amy Adams 演出既語言學家Louise(between Amy成日做Louise)，被軍方邀請，協助調查突然到訪地球唔同國家既12架太空船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUOFj13.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUOFj13.gif&h=33807303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軍方同政府可以每日定時出入太空船，雖然每次出入都消曬毒咁，但入面無任何有害物，最後Amy同外星人傾計，學識外星人語言，識用外星語言思考，問到外星人係想黎幫地球人。<br />\n呢種外星人係<strong>非線性思考</strong>既生物，即係佢地係無因果概念，因為佢地本身已經知道過去同未來會發生既事，佢地既語言同文字都係，唔係直線書寫，而係一個圓形既圖案，從任何一個方向開始閱讀都會得到同一個結果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nz6fpv9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNz6fpv9.png&h=8eadbc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外星人foresee到自己三千年後需要人類幫助，所以宜家黎幫左人類先。<br />\n最後全球12隻外星人既太空船之中，係中國果到果隻比中國人宣戰，Louise因為識外星語言，用外星語言思考時間，洞悉左未來，打電話比中國將軍，講出佢老婆既遺言，<strong>&ldquo;In war there are no winners, only widows.&rdquo;</strong><strong>沒有炒賣，就沒有殺害</strong><a href=\"https://www.thrillist.com/entertainment/nation/arrival-chinese-line-ending\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thrillist.com%2Fentertainment%2Fnation%2Farrival-chinese-line-ending&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=d48b82f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thrillist.com/entertainment/nation/arrival-chinese-line-ending</a><br />\n最後收兵Bbq<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，電影中插敘佢同個女既日常生活事。個女出世、畫畫、玩遊戲、做功課，同Louise既感情好好，最後生癌死左，Louise都係佢身邊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e77392be3e5f513fc48f8750cc086342a7c1323","tid":1115052,"uid":74778,"like":45,"dislike":5,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">重點影評部分黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後我真係成個人震懾左，用科學角度講有關<strong>時間</strong>既故事，一向都好吸引，好似interstellar 咁，不過nolan真係係講故事方面太出色，令佢煽情既部分唔夠突出(雖然父女同齡對話果到我喊到仆街)<br />\n<br />\nArrival無interstella咁複雜，精而簡，而且佢講既命題都相當大。我對於網上搵到既一d影評都幾失望，10篇影評得一篇有提到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">襌</span></strong>既概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面果張太空船既劇照，第一眼已經feel到好強烈既襌既感覺，雲海 太空船:河流 石春<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjGSSBW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjGSSBW.png&h=1fe6e7b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襌同佛唔一定有關，襌可以係<strong>順應自然</strong>，同呢套電影本身既主題好有關係，就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人類係線性思考生物，有因有果，但如果你有100%預知能力，能夠非線性思考，無所謂因果，你本身已經知道你既結局，你既故事，你仲有無自由去選擇你既路？你會唔會去令你既故事按劇本進行？<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n作者係用外星人、語言去做表達既工具。外星人本身唔係重點，網上影評基本上有一半都係話好悶，因為講到明話本身諗住去睇打外星怪死光槍蕉蕉蕉，點知悶到仆街。其實成套戲無論係<strong>細節、演技、畫面、意義</strong>都係一流。<br />\n<br />\n用水墨畫做外星文字基礎<br />\n圓形文字代表無論任何角度都係同樣結果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AfcSPF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AfcSPF.gif&h=ab7456fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UioNGKc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUioNGKc.png&h=a2d02e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都充滿住東方哲學既襌味<br />\n<br />\n對於<strong>決定論同自由意志</strong>之間既爭論不休，好多藝術作品，例如電影 小說 詩詞，都有提出問題同嘗試解答，不過好多都會好低手咁變左正能樣。但arrival唔止，佢提出問題既方法係用Louise知道自己將要同Ian結婚生女又離婚女又生癌，最後都係得返自己一個，一個咁既結果，比你你仲會唔會繼續令你既將來發生？Louise會，因為<strong>我地不能因為生命既悲劇而否定生命;而係用堅持生命既決心，去肯定生命既悲劇，因為生命既悲劇係生命既一部分。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMvPVeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMvPVeo.png&h=16c82257&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQNVQNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQNVQNJ.png&h=d8ccca4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GjYxS03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGjYxS03.png&h=aa9827a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abgC37K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabgC37K.png&h=f95d0d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lnv01Up.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnv01Up.png&h=47c31f53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSDJZF5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSDJZF5.png&h=8c44b6fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZP3uaNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZP3uaNL.png&h=6e10e08d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8cF1Ur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8cF1Ur.png&h=52c4d705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔好屌太大力，netfilx cap圖得字幕。不過都get到講野既係Louise同Ian啦</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個電影原著係姜峯楠既小說<em>你一生的故事 the story of your life</em>。電影透過12架太空船，代表聖經入面12門徒，帶神既說話(文字)比人類，令人類(Louise)知道生命的意義。係人類既角度，人就用住呢個人生態度，去順應自然，因為人始終係線性思考生物:<em><strong>就算我知道將來必然發生既悲劇例如死亡，我都會勇於執行生命</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n個感覺似係鬼佬角度去睇東方哲學，因為睇姜峯楠既短篇小說，好多都係呢個feel，例如有一篇係巴別塔高到去到天頂個底，鑿上去通返去地底海床，再去返塔底。有種因為<strong>直線地追求神而發現世界循環不息既曲線</strong><br />\n<br />\n講返Arrival，外星人係有目的既，就係要同人類交好，將來可以互助。但其實我認為咁樣既安排，令到本身係無因無果，無所謂目的而生存而做事既外星人變得有目的，佢地因為想被救，所以黎搵人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為小說既軍人想知道外星人黎地球既目的，但到小說最後發現班外星人係真係無目的咁走左。咁會切合多d個主題，但電影咁拍就大鑊，會連僅餘既高潮都無埋。<br />\n<br />\n演技方面Amy 真係無得彈，一路都好鐘意佢，今次既發揮相當稱職，不過做個有決心既學者，慈母都做得入型入格<br />\n<br />\nJeremy好啱做呢d傻仔毒撚<br />\n<br />\n我有因為呢套戲太正所以買姜峯楠既原著小說，Forest做既麻撚煩軍官，係同小說入面一撚樣，淨係諗結果，Amy同Jeremy講既學術原因乜都唔柒聽，話鳩知你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括黎講我係比10分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢個命題吸引，其次係佢個手法同靚到震懾人既畫面。各個細節都有關有意義，真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd2d80222b5df6149c0714cb9355dfcd4079601","tid":1115052,"uid":159183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"太有深度<br />\n睇唔明<br />\n但樓主解得好好"},{"pid":"6bbaa481d7ae34cfd96e5e81c7064a8adfef393c","tid":1115052,"uid":218823,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:04:09.000Z","msg":"去到尾段先揭曉多啲 呼應返開頭女主角獨白 好正<br />\n畫面好靚 特別鍾意啲外星文字<br />\n我嗰陣睇完套戲仲即刻諗住生女要叫hannah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88836c5bb9a78760c4b5ac56a381bde3abac5f5","tid":1115052,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6bbaa481d7ae34cfd96e5e81c7064a8adfef393c","tid":1115052,"uid":218823,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:04:09.000Z","msg":"去到尾段先揭曉多啲 呼應返開頭女主角獨白 好正<br />\n畫面好靚 特別鍾意啲外星文字<br />\n我嗰陣睇完套戲仲即刻諗住生女要叫hannah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HfgDuG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HfgDuG.png&h=35a8defe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好浪漫，對自然既追求"},{"pid":"9969dac7603f8e7e120b9be97a61244f5e6ef7c4","tid":1115052,"uid":7332,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"好文但下次可以叫人慎入先,有劇透"},{"pid":"8b0f83d971e4841f080b3751d7e3f5f9a89ce0c9","tid":1115052,"uid":45627,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"淨係頭5分鐘同最尾嗰段獨白已經滿分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個結局真係估佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6786002e0bd42b550cd54a17bdb9f2cab271df36","tid":1115052,"uid":21896,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:10:37.000Z","msg":"上個星期睇左....頂唔順係咁skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2135cc8dd590bee4351683cc0072f7a4fd365a","tid":1115052,"uid":2972,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"終於有人講呢套<br />\n我自己好鍾意呢套戲<br />\n巴打解得好好<br />\n套戲無論畫面, 劇情, 文字都好正<br />\n尤其解外星文字嗰part 真係啱曬我呢啲現實科幻撚口味<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我覺得有時啲戲係比中文譯名害咗<br />\n你改天煞異降好難怪人唔以為打外星人片<br />\n間接令當時票房同評價都唔好"},{"pid":"0b7ef9557147aa2f713add8f44a955b150f45c0d